{"type": "article", "id": 56918, "title": "刘昊然代言科颜氏，iPhone XS Max 新广告大到不行 | 乙方日报", "description": "这里有营销和营销人相关的一切", "date": "2018-09-29T04:45:33Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 64, "name": "广告"}, {"id": 68, "name": "苹果"}, {"id": 23359, "name": "科颜氏"}, {"id": 1297, "name": "阿迪达斯"}, {"id": 53110, "name": "刘昊然"}], "category": 18, "column": 31, "author": 103970, "comment_count": 15, "praise_count": 39, "image": "img/article/article_show/20180929124056Wo9KTelr0c8a6R43.jpeg", "contents": "<h3 finallycleanhtml=\"true\" nocleanhtml=\"true\">明星又代言了啥</h3><p><a href=\"https://weibo.com/kiehlschina\" rel=\"nofollow\"><strong>科颜氏宣布刘昊然为品牌代言人。</strong></a>第一波上线的短片卖的产品是牛油果眼霜（太合适了）。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201809291221477V8hxQuN9DYBknJX.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.407246\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-embeds\"> <figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <iframe frameborder=\"0\" src=\"https://v.qq.com/txp/iframe/player.html?vid=g0720hvjwoi\"></iframe> </figure> </div><h3>值得一提的 Case</h3><p><strong>苹果 iPhone XS Max 最新广告&nbsp;Growth Spurt。</strong>一切你爱的都大，更大。</p><div class=\"com-insert-embeds\"> <figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <iframe frameborder=\"0\" src=\"https://v.qq.com/txp/iframe/player.html?vid=w0723etoz5j\"></iframe> </figure> </div><p><strong><a href=\"https://www.digitaling.com/projects/39969.html\" rel=\"nofollow\">阿迪达斯找了三个“街头文化的串联者”来卖最新推的老爹鞋&nbsp;YUNG 96</a></strong>，分别是 Milk杂志主编 Kevin＆FightClub 中文站主编 Penny，Randomevent 品牌创始人Younker，以及 InventoryPool 创始人 Aka。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201809291225448TSnmk70gafR5MBu.gif\" data-ratio=\"0.563333\" data-format=\"gif\"> </figure></div><p><a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=-I_CIy3Uqx0\" rel=\"nofollow\"><strong>Google 20 周年上线了一个纪念 Doodle</strong></a>，通过搜索内容来看过去二十年来世界的变化。</p><div class=\"com-insert-embeds\"> <figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <iframe frameborder=\"0\" src=\"https://v.qq.com/txp/iframe/player.html?vid=u07201rqxoq\"></iframe> </figure> </div><p><strong><a href=\"&lt;iframe frameborder=&quot;0&quot; src=&quot;https://v.qq.com/txp/iframe/player.html?vid=h0719ie3ic1&quot; allowFullScreen=&quot;true&quot;&gt;&lt;/iframe&gt;\" rel=\"nofollow\">百度 AR 实景导航广告</a></strong>，把一个通常很无聊的 APP 功能广告拍得算是有趣。平时这样的场景还发生的少吗？！</p><div class=\"com-insert-embeds\"> <figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <iframe frameborder=\"0\" src=\"https://v.qq.com/txp/iframe/player.html?vid=h0719ie3ic1\"></iframe> </figure> </div><p><a href=\"https://adage.com/article/media/true-gritty-a-myst-nhl-mascot-won-internet/315073/\" rel=\"nofollow\"><strong>美国冰球联盟 NHL 发布了一个诡异的新吉祥物</strong></a>。结果反响和讨论度还不错，据说这个路数是为了吸引年轻人。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201809291235078Y2Q5zGXIpAEkOsv.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.368627\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><h3>其他，也挺重要</h3><p><strong><a href=\"https://www.thedrum.com/news/2018/09/28/accenture-interactive-revenue-reportedly-grew-more-20-last-year\" rel=\"nofollow\">埃森哲互动的收入去年增长了 20%。</a></strong>在财报会议上埃森哲的首席财务官 David P Rowland 透露了这一点，称公司对旗下这个新营销部门的表现“特别满意”。</p><p>题图来自科颜氏</p>"}